        <Parent_String>warp pile weave [300227932], pile weave (textile) [300227872], textile materials by weaving technique [300231684], textile materials by process or technique [300231603], textile materials [300231565], fiber by product [300014062], fiber and fiber by product [300014023], materials by physical form [300247256], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
